Well, good afternoon.

00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:28.060
Good afternoon, everybody,
and welcome to the African

00:00:28.060 --> 00:00:30.220
and Middle East Division.

00:00:30.220 --> 00:00:33.430
I'm Mary-Jane Deeb,
Chief of the Division.

00:00:33.430 --> 00:00:37.130
And I'm delighted to
see you all here.

00:00:37.130 --> 00:00:42.990
We always start the program with
a sort of general introduction

00:00:42.990 --> 00:00:47.590
about our division and what we do.

00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:52.950 position:56%
