our division for many more programs.

00:00:52.950 --> 00:00:56.750
So, this division is
responsible for the collections

00:00:56.750 --> 00:01:03.420
from 78 different countries,
the entire continent of Africa,

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:07.990
the Middle East, Central
Asia, and the Caucasus.

00:01:07.990 --> 00:01:13.360
And we are divided into three
sections, the African section,

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:20.270
the Hebraic Section, and we collect
worldwide for the Hebraic section,

00:01:20.270 --> 00:01:23.150
and the Near East section.

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:29.250
We serve collections in the
languages of the region.

