And I will explain this in a
minute, but our collections,

00:01:34.810 --> 00:01:40.310
very custodial collection,
and custodian division,

00:01:40.310 --> 00:01:42.820 position:56%
and our materials are in the scripts

00:01:42.820 --> 00:01:44.740
and the languages of
these countries.

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:49.870
So, were you to do
research on Ethiopia,

00:01:49.870 --> 00:01:54.460
the materials in [foreign name],
in [foreign name], would be here,

00:01:54.460 --> 00:01:59.120 position:56%
