00:39:44.490 --> 00:39:48.080
which gave great symbolic
importance to the church.

00:39:48.080 --> 00:39:52.520
So, the -- and the church, the
role of the church in fostering

00:39:52.520 --> 00:39:55.680
that Ethiopian sense of
identity, can't be underestimated.

00:39:55.680 --> 00:40:00.230
Even its impact on
non-Christian elements

00:40:00.230 --> 00:40:02.920
of Ethiopian society
has been profound

00:40:02.920 --> 00:40:06.970
because it does give a
sense of timelessness

00:40:06.970 --> 00:40:10.250
to the whole Ethiopian society.

00:40:10.250 --> 00:40:13.890
So, it's perhaps in a
sense, the iconography

00:40:13.890 --> 00:40:18.390
of Ethiopia has been less
physical, than say the Roman

00:40:18.390 --> 00:40:25.950
and Hellenic civilizations, or even
the British sense of construction

00:40:25.950 --> 00:40:31.580
