00:54:02.990 --> 00:54:07.010
And one of the things that we're
seeing around the world today,

00:54:07.010 --> 00:54:09.500
is this cry from most societies,

00:54:09.500 --> 00:54:12.000
"We want our country
back," whatever that means.

00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:14.060
And I don't think most people know
what it means, or they know --

00:54:14.060 --> 00:54:20.340
they want to know that their whole
purpose, their ancestry and so on,

00:54:20.340 --> 00:54:23.810
has some meaning, not to
just start fresh again.

00:54:23.810 --> 00:54:25.110
We saw with the collapse --

00:54:25.110 --> 00:54:28.830
well, the collapse of the Soviet
Union 70 years after the decree

00:54:28.830 --> 00:54:31.510
that it a new Soviet
man would be created.

00:54:31.510 --> 00:54:33.690
Seventy years later with the
collapse of the Communist Party

00:54:33.690 --> 00:54:37.200
in the Soviet Union, we
saw an absolute revival

00:54:37.200 --> 00:54:40.230
