suppressed for 70 years.

00:54:40.230 --> 00:54:41.530
The church.

00:54:41.530 --> 00:54:48.900
The iconic, Russian
construction styles.

00:54:48.900 --> 00:54:53.150
The reverence for the
monarchy of the past.

00:54:53.150 --> 00:54:55.390
Certainly, the past always
carries with it a lot of baggage,

00:54:55.390 --> 00:55:01.040
but it also, as does
our individual history,

00:55:01.040 --> 00:55:03.700
we have the good and
the bad within us.

00:55:03.700 --> 00:55:06.350
And, but it's ours.

